In Section~\ref{sec:Rmore} we prove Theorems~\ref{theo:hasanunboundedcomponent} and~\ref{theo:hasnounboundedcomponent}. Then, in Section~\ref{sec:R1}, we prove Theorems~\ref{theo:R1irrational}, \ref{theo:R1uncountable} and~\ref{theo:R1open}. Finally, in Section~\ref{sec:examples} we give all the examples mentioned above.












